{"tid":773361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗自己 教育廢中廢老 諗唔諗得過？","createTime":"2018-08-09T12:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T16:46:43.000Z","uid":114275,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"507688ecbbda3a6fc8fc7c0e681ab7c35a9b9656","tid":773361,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"150 大家都知道禍害幾深<br />\n<br />\n但除咗屌鳩港共之外<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過由源頭減廢？<br />\n<br />\n廢中廢老再培訓 <br />\n<br />\n避免直接指出大陸閪嘅陰毒<br />\n<br />\n改為曲線宣傳香港制度入面大陸閪經常會用嘅漏洞<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n<br />\n離婚分居房署幾乎一定會判間屋俾個女人<br />\n<br />\n老屈男人打仔幾乎一定成立<br />\n<br />\n如果有不良嗜好如酗酒老屈男人入精神科極容易<br />\n<br />\n希望廢中廢老明白 大陸閪屌得 但唔好娶落嚟<br />\n<br />\n諗唔諗得過？<br />\n<br />\n連登咁多高人 請出招"},{"pid":"223eeae3c62c4de14f269f471482fab814775343","tid":773361,"uid":19978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"你叫唔醒裝睡的人"},{"pid":"7bfba963bfed8e56bce3ac6f9952970f310b0f50","tid":773361,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223eeae3c62c4de14f269f471482fab814775343","tid":773361,"uid":19978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"你叫唔醒裝睡的人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"工作關係 <br />\n<br />\n我發現都有一定數量嘅人係真心唔知道大陸閪原來有咩招可以用"},{"pid":"6b756005324cde7bd00bf34ccb230a16ab6d06fe","tid":773361,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e49e84d44442a4108412fbd4240f1359b3793488","tid":773361,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1afb95e942749865e98016832b7a343b8a2a17a","tid":773361,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"廢老會覺得悲劇不會發生在自己身上"}]}